title: Isoball (Gold Edition) v1.0
description:
Use the blocks, arrows, ramps, bridges, etc. that are provided in the area at the bottom to build a track for the ball to get to the hole without falling and breaking. 

Repeatedly click an object in the bottom area to rotate it. Drag the block to place it. Click erase then click on the block twice to remove it

- Beautiful 3D graphics.
- Ability to rotate camera.
- All 75 Levels + 36 Extra Levels + Sandbox Levels.
- Realistic physics.

If you liked this game on PC now it's your chance to enjoy it offline and with even much more fun.

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.evolgames.isoisogold
